{"tid":1258880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反分化] 陳雲：一定要爭取到立法會普選。我們或者會互相吵鬧，但大家一定要努力。","createTime":"2019-06-26T10:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T13:45:38.000Z","uid":131171,"like":164,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"baf345b6f056c1b634cb2efba6fad9f14862c245","tid":1258880,"uid":131171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"陳雲：美國將立法敦促香港政府在2020年立法會普選。<br />\n大家香港人，這幾日一定要努力，集會請願，向國際社會求助。<span style=\"color: red;\">我們或者會互相吵鬧，沒所謂的，但大家一定要努力。這種千載難逢的機會，香港歷史上好少出現。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>民主外送來了！ 美國會修法：限香港立法會2020年普選</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2833406?fbclid=IwAR3kc8_fjt5n3IICs3d_8Hr6M0nrKN3-HSRWQKt_BI0eh64gFtBOEBVqSds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2833406%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3kc8_fjt5n3IICs3d_8Hr6M0nrKN3-HSRWQKt_BI0eh64gFtBOEBVqSds&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmXHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=db88e2a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2833406%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3kc8_fjt5n3IICs3d_8Hr6M0nrKN3-HSRWQKt_BI0eh64gFtBOEBVqSds&h=840959f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2833406?fbclid=IwAR3kc8_fjt5n3IICs3d_8Hr6M0nrKN3-HSRWQKt_BI0eh64gFtBOEBVqSds</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin <span style=\"color: red;\">到時好多議席，大家爭個飽。但首先，一定要爭取到立法會普選。</span>"},{"pid":"aa8f436508efe22ab19470d86a1cbe924287944a","tid":1258880,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":62,"score":-57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:21:08.000Z","msg":"《香港人權與民主法案》點計都唔關云伯事<br />\n<br />\n青山派收皮啦"},{"pid":"1ec6fbf21d41db82def5510a6a766f1954d08c2f","tid":1258880,"uid":131171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a32404ae22fa96ae60ebe833026e3daaf2d7fec","tid":1258880,"uid":67151,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"